lead_paragraph: A 30-day stay on an orbiting lab would set a national record as part of a program to visit the moon in 2025.

headline.print_headline: China Launches Astronauts on Its Longest Space Mission
headline.main: China Launches 2 Astronauts on Its Longest Space Mission

snippet: A 30-day stay on an orbiting lab would set a national record as part of a program to visit the moon in 2025....
abstract: China launches manned spacecraft with two astronauts to deliver supplies to orbiting space lab; astronauts are expected to stay aloft for 30 days, country's longest space mission.
